276
00:16:37.038 --> 00:16:38.498
And he watched her.

277
00:16:40.959 --> 00:16:42.711
Secretly.

278
00:16:42.752 --> 00:16:45.338
Watched her play for two days.

279
00:16:45.380 --> 00:16:47.215
