It was insane.

286
00:17:05.650 --> 00:17:08.611
But there was no
other explanation.

287
00:17:11.823 --> 00:17:12.823
So...

288
00:17:14.451 --> 00:17:16.453
so it's true.

289
00:17:21.041 --> 00:17:22.125
That's...

290
00:17:25.211 --> 00:17:27.756
- That's...
