363
00:20:19.469 --> 00:20:20.637
Charlie.

364
00:20:22.389 --> 00:20:24.808
Charlie. (groans)

365
00:20:27.644 --> 00:20:30.271
How can you not see
that this is a...

366
00:20:31.147 --> 00:20:32.774
