412
00:22:16.878 --> 00:22:18.718
You guys making some
money on a nice fucking...

413
00:22:18.755 --> 00:22:21.049
Jerry. Hey. Hey.
you stupid asshole.

414
00:22:21.091 --> 00:22:23.176
