418
00:22:28.098 --> 00:22:29.265
God. man.

419
00:22:29.307 --> 00:22:31.476
Oh. this is. this is
what we're doing. huh?

420
00:22:31.518 --> 00:22:33.561
Get the fuck... (grunts)

421
00:22:33.603 --> 00:22:34.854
Get off of me!

422
