469
00:24:13.370 --> 00:24:14.496
Man. it just...

470
00:24:15.705 --> 00:24:16.664
It pisses me off.

471
00:24:16.706 --> 00:24:17.999
I know.

472
00:24:18.041 --> 00:24:19.626
