cost in a weekend.

491
00:25:07.298 --> 00:25:09.759
To them. it's a
drip in the bucket.

492
00:25:09.801 --> 00:25:11.594
They're whales.

493
00:25:11.636 --> 00:25:14.764
But Caine is our Moby Dick.

494
00:25:16.266 --> 00:25:18.059
When my dad handed me
the keys to this place.

495
00:25:18.101 --> 00:25:19.436
